  "timing": "Schedule outreach during working hours in the relevant regions (North America, Europe, Asia), initiating contact over 1-2 weeks with spaced follow-ups every 5-7 days. Leverage mid-morning and early-afternoon periods for higher engagement, and synchronize outreach with industry-specific milestones, fiscal cycles, or events to increase relevance. Adjust timing seasonally based on industry activity and avoid holiday or slow holiday periods for maximum receptivity.",
